Album - Class in edu.usfca.cs
Album is the class to create Album objects for the library Extends the Entity class Has three different constructors Uses setters and getters to retrieve instances of the object To write a file or send a request to a third party data provider it can create following formats: XML, HTML, JSON To write/read from the music.db it creates the right format with the methods: toSQL, fromSQL
